  "texts": [
    "GCC (GTAV Crowd Counting) was generated using GTAV.",
    "It consists of 15,212 images containing a total of 7,625,843 pedestrians, collected from 100 scenes and 4 different views per scene.",
    "Each image has a resolution of 1080 × 1920 pixels and contains, on average, 501 people.",
    "Moreover, different lighting conditions have been considered according to different daytime hours (e.g., 9-12) and weather conditions (e.g., extra sunny, rain).",
    "Pedestrians have been rendered using 256 different human models with 6 different clothing appearances."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}